platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.ta.k: Tasks that keep you on track

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Put your to-dos in TickTick, and boom: Theyre all in perfect order. This all-in-one organizer is a personal assistant for your brain, one that eases the mental strain of All That Stuff To Do by elegantly organizing it, which lets you focus less on deadlines and more on the big picture. Put it right to work as a refined (and visually pleasing) to-do list, or make use of power features like its Eisenhower Matrix, which automatically plots your tasks on a chart in terms of urgency and importance, or the built-in Pomodoro timer, which keeps you properly balanced between productivity and burnout. People dont just want a task manager, says founder Damon Woo. They want to manage everything in their lives.
A personal assistant for your brain. Refine your to-do list, prioritise your tasks on a chart or use the built-in Pomodoro timer to keep you balanced between productivity and burnout.
